articles.title: Boland Park Paarl Weather Report For SA vs IND 3rd ODI - OneCricket
articles.description: The series is levelled at 1-1 and the decider at Boland Park in Paarl is expected to be a cracking encounter. So, before the game gets underway, let's look at the weather report for the third ODI between South Africa and India.
